data.description: BRAND NEW FLOORS ON MAIN LEVEL! From the moment you enter the home, the possibilities are endless! A formal living room greets you but could be turned into Aa home office! A dining room is also at the front of the home w/ access to kitchen. The kitchen features granite countertops, glass tile backsplash, SS appliances, and eat-in-kitchen. Family room is nestled at the back of the home and features a fireplace w/ mantel. Head up the stairs where you will find the primary suite w/ ensuite bath, three additional bedrooms, and a full bath. The primary bedroom has vaulted ceilings and a sitting room that could be used as home office, gym, or reading nook. Ensuite bath features a tiled shower, double vanity, & soaking tub. Exterior of home features a concrete patio, fenced in yard, storage shed, and private wooded lot! Newer HVAC unit. Great location in Legacy Park which has an outdoor pool, playground, clubhouse, & more! All conveniently located to shops & restaurants in Indian Land!
